\section{Version 1.12.0}{
  \itemize{
    \item End of release cycle for deprecated functions, moved to the addGraph/getGraph related methods.
    \item Deprecated plugin builder methods have been removed.
  }
}

\section{Version 1.10.0}{
  \itemize{
    \item Improved graph attribute settings and interface.
  }
}

\section{Version 1.8.0}{
  \itemize{
    \item Improved compatibility with igraph objects.
    \item Additional arrow options to deal with directed graph associations.
  }
}

\section{Version 1.6.0}{
  \itemize{
    \item Interface simplification: several deprecated low-level functions were moved to the addGraph/getGraph related methods.
    \item Dependency changed from igraph to igraph0.
    \item Re-established conection with igraph.
  }
}

\section{Version 1.4.0}{
  \itemize{
    \item All graph attributes are now set via addGraph/getGraph methods.
    \item Improved loading performance: better xml serialization, data packing and post formats.
    \item Some routines are simplified for better maintenance. 
  }
}

\section{Version 1.2.0}{
  \itemize{
    \item Improved loading performance, xml serialization, data packing and post formats.
    \item Improved server/client connection.
    \item Improved control over the app main features from R.
    \item Correction/fine-tune of dynamic layout function under zoom-in/zoom-out requests.
    \item Legend function is fixed for node/edge shape attributes.
  }
}

\section{Version 1.0.0}{
  \itemize{
    \item 1st release of RedeR [2011-03-23].
  }
}


